# What is Kramdowm #
转换器：markdown->HTML，除了支持markdown最基本的语法，还对其进行了扩展。

# create TOC #
Change in `_config.yml`

	markdown: kramdown
	...
	kramdown:
		auto_ids: true
		footnote_nr: 1
		entity_output: as_char
		toc_levels: 1..6
		use_coderay: false
		parse_block_html: true

The Table of Content work easily with just : (and with some css adjustment)
	* toc
